{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736620/extras/customImage2.png?t=1731272299\" /><br>Journey through the serene depths of an ancient forest and explore the sacred temple that cradles profound wisdom and complex challenges. <br><br>The Eightfold Path is an immersive puzzle and exploration adventure steeped in the teachings of Buddhism, inviting you to embark on a quest towards enlightenment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736620/extras/customImage0.png?t=1731272299\" /><br>To reach the ultimate state of pure bliss, you must navigate through the labyrinth of desires and suffering that obscures true harmony. <br><br>Nature, a steadfast companion on your journey, will guide you. Yet, the true challenge lies in confronting the fears and inner demons that dwell within you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736620/extras/meditate-export.gif?t=1731272299\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meditation</h2>In moments of unrest, seek solace in meditation. Find a tranquil refuge, sit down, and take a moment to unwind. Focus on your breath, feel the rhythms of your body, and release the transient thoughts that flutter through your mind.<br><br><i>The Eightfold Path is calling. Will you embrace the teachings, conquer the trials, and unlock the path towards enlightenment?</i>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Eightfold Path","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1736620/847492660ccfa4a30f3e0b97febdd0186e732057.jpg"},{"name":"Path to Wisdom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1736620/9691f88311a83f9a672b405178589065f0c4da08.jpg"},{"name":"The Four Thoughts","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1736620/0c0e319049e3e0346803d38ab0de201d24185945.jp